snippet: Karrie Webb won her first L.P.G.A. Tour title in two years, rallying from five shots down for a two-shot win over Shanshan Feng at the ShopRite L.P.G.A. Classic in Galloway Township, N.J.
abstract: Karrie Webb wins her first LPGA Tour title in two years, rallying from five shots down for a two-shot win at the ShopRite LPGA Classic in Galloway Township, NJ; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Karrie Webb won her first L.P.G.A. Tour title in two years, rallying from five shots down for a two-shot win over Shanshan Feng at the ShopRite L.P.G.A. Classic in Galloway Township, N.J.
